      "title": "Cylinders waiting around the empty playground",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Test match between the touring Australian cricket team and the Sri Lankan team will begin tomorrow (29) at the Galle International Cricket Stadium.",
        "Around the grounds, yellow and blue colored cooking gas empty cylinders are lined up.",
        "It is noteworthy that all these cylinders have been lined up there for more than 25 days."
